### Welcome to GitHub Pages.

This project is the ejb module for [InventoryBeer_GUI](https://github.com/nkenna/InventoryBeer_GUI) (GUI), [InventoryBeer-JSF](https://github.com/nkenna/repo-InventoryBeer-JSF) (JSF) and [InventoryBeer-WS](https://github.com/nkenna/repo-inventoryBeer-ws) (Web Service).
